# Lockstep: one observation in -> one 7-D action out (the lerobot policy's
# internal chunk queue re-predicts when empty, exactly as eval_*.predict).
# images[0] is ALWAYS the system camera; extra images (3cam SmolVLA) carry
# their scene-camera name in header.frame_id and are mapped by policy_node.
uint64 obs_seq
bool reset_queue     # true on the first call of an episode (policy.reset())
sensor_msgs/Image[] images
float64[] state      # [flange xyz, vac_prev] — the recording-frame state
string instruction
---
bool ok
kr6_msgs/ActionChunk chunk   # chunk_len=1
